::Prowl::

Prowl yells out in pain as Iron Raptor's teeth go all the way through his 
hand, and come out the other side, the acid burning through the armor that 
wasn't pierced. Her jerking back his arm and slamming her paws into his chest 
at the same time nearly snaps off his arm, a couple of nasty-sounding snaps 
coming from it. Prowl gritts his teeth in pain as claws dig into his chest, 
mechfluid flowing out of the wounds.

This was something he least expected: his mate attacking him after he was 
nearly killed by a 45-foot tall gestalt. Perhaps this was her way of getting 
him back for worrying her.

"Love, what are you doing?" he says in a strained voice, his good arm taking 
hold of one of her forelegs and trying to push it away from his chest. He 
jerks his other hand back, the acid-weakened metal tearing one her teeth. 
Prowl's arm goes limp as he pulls it out of Iron Raptor's mouth, leaking 
mechfluid, its moving mechanism completely disabled.
